## MinimalImportableIdentifier type

Represents the minimum amount of information needed to import an [IIdentifier](./core.iidentifier.md)

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
export declare type MinimalImportableIdentifier = {
    keys: Array<MinimalImportableKey>;
    services?: Array<IService>;
} & Omit<IIdentifier, 'keys' | 'services'>;
```
